sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Outbox as Payment Outbox
    participant Kafka
    participant Processor as Payment Processor
    participant Order as Order Service (Saga)
    participant Ledger
    participant Risk as Risk Engine
    participant Balance
    participant Notification
    participant Merchant

    Note over Outbox,Merchant: HTTP request has already returned 202 Accepted

    %% ----------------------------------------------------
    %% Payment Processing
    %% ----------------------------------------------------

    Outbox->>Kafka: Publish PaymentInitiated

    Kafka->>Processor: PaymentInitiated

    Processor->>Processor: Simulate Gateway Processing

    alt Payment Successful

        Processor->>Kafka: PaymentCompleted

        Kafka->>Order: PaymentCompleted

        %% Ledger
        Order->>Ledger: RecordLedgerEntry

        Ledger->>Kafka: LedgerEntryRecorded

        Kafka->>Order: LedgerEntryRecorded

        %% Eligibility
        Order->>Risk: CheckPayoutEligibility

        Risk-->>Order: EligibilityApproved

        %% Balance
        Order->>Balance: ReserveBalance

        Balance->>Kafka: BalanceReserved

        Kafka->>Order: BalanceReserved

        %% Notification
        Order->>Notification: NotifyMerchant

        Notification->>Merchant: Payment Notification

        Notification->>Kafka: MerchantNotified

        Kafka->>Order: MerchantNotified

        Note over Order: Saga Completed

    else Payment Failed

        Processor->>Kafka: PaymentFailed

        Kafka->>Order: PaymentFailed

        Note over Order: Saga Ends (No Compensation Required)

    end